@voidheremking I'm sorry that someone has to say it but improving his gas tank is not plausible. He's still a top competitor and definitely top 5-10 best featherweights in the world, but his gas tank is not something he can improve as he's on a clear physical decline, which has big impact on his cardio and durability. He's still improving technically, especially in terms of striking, but he has reached his physical limit a long time ago.

